\zoli1 \bd Ubaka inzu yawe n’umwete n’uk\bd*\bd witanga, ehe bugira bwire ncuti\bd*\bd ; niwamburwa urusago rwawe rwo mw’isi ntuz’usange uri gusa, nawe ncuti.\bd*
